sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Library UI
  participant GW as Gateway
  participant LS as user-library-service
  participant US as user-service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant BS as book-service
  participant AN as analytics

  UI->>GW: POST /api/library/reading-lists/move-books
  GW->>LS: move request(sourceList,targetList,bookIds)
  LS->>US: verify token
  US-->>LS: userId
  LS->>DB: lock/check source+target ownership
  LS->>DB: delete from source junction rows
  LS->>DB: insert into target junction rows(avoid duplicates)
  LS->>BS: fetch moved book details(optional enrichment)
  BS-->>LS: book metadata subset
  LS->>AN: emit READING_LIST_BOOKS_MOVED
  LS-->>UI: updated source+target summaries
